n 2500 elements and it take time to display them.\r\n</li><li>When I open the top expander, it take all the available space and it is not possible to open the other expanders anymore.\r\n</li><li>When I resize the windows, the datagrids don't resize at all. </li></ol>\r\n<p>Since I am new to WPF, any help would be really appreciated.</p>\r\n<p>Christophe</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n",
